Dr Neelam is a very warm and approachable doctor. My family and I only consult with her as our GP and her medication always works for us. Her warm nature and patience listening to every patient is truly commendable. She was a God sent to us when my mother had to go into emergency for Hernia and Dr Neelam herself ensured my mother got the best treatment at an unusual hour. I would highly recommend Dr Neelam and have referred her to several of my friends and colleagues.
